Body: Description: I'm trying to download the file from the client portal and I'm getting an error saying I need to open a ticket.
SLA is violated, because ticket was from the US timezone, high priority with small SLA, and the US engineer is currently on vacation.
What We've Learned Updated: Provided their PingCastle license.
Next Steps Updated: Wait for customer confirmation that the license is working and there is nothing else to assist
